Hi Andrew,

Please keep the mailing list in cc.

The estimates in mc are the differences of the parameter estimates (betas) between both levels. E.g. 5.LR -1.LR = -1.168 or 5.LR = 1.LR - 1.168

summary(mc) should give you the significance of those differences. That should work. If it doesn't, please provide more info: at least your code and the error message. A small reproducible example is better.
confint(mc) gives the confidence intervals of the differences.

